reviewText: I expected more from this video. It's not bad, just not as sexy as the cover would lead you to believe.

90 minutes of the same girl getting pampered. Video quality is absolute junk, it looks like they shot it with a picture phone that they couldn't get to focus. This movie is not worth the blu ray disk its on, don't hit that order button trust me i wish someone had posted a comment like this before i bought it. this director must hate everyone

From the Anime Maki review:  Thai Relax is a solid gravure title that Ayaka Uchiyama fans will want to check out. She's a hot model for starters and if that isn't reason enough this release offers plenty of compromising, sexy shots. The picture quality is probably the best I've seen from Happy Chicken Pink, and it's right up there with Ayaka is Your Angel. A clean image, sharp details, and solid lighting help make several moments in this release stand out. It's one of Happy Chicken Pink's best efforts and leaves you looking forward to Ayaka's next release. Check it out!
I brought this DVD because of the cover.  Cute girl but not what I thought.
